title: The Secret of the Key: A Sixty-Eight Rooms Adventure
description:
Chicago sixth graders Ruthie and Jack think they’ve learned everything about the magic of the Art Institute’s Thorne Rooms. But the magic starts to act strangely when Ruthie and Jack discover two rings that are out of place—and out of time.  Unlock the magic in the exciting conclusion to the Sixty-Eight Rooms Adventures! Middle Grade (8-12).

Paperback, 256 pages.
